│ operations.\n\nThe issue arises during the cleanup phase of                 │
│ `GeneratedRTChecks`. The `GeneratedRTChecks` destructor attempts to clean   │
│ up both SCEV and memory check expanders, but the memory check cleanup code  │
│ assumes that if `MemRuntimeCheckCond` exists, then `MemCheckBlock` also     │
