│                                                                             │
│ So if the expander hoists a computation to `entry`, that instruction would  │
│ be in `entry` and might be used by existing code.                           │
│                                                                             │
│ This would violate the invariant.                                           │
│                                                                             │
│ The solution is to ensure that when we clean up, we also clean up any       │
